Season 7 is an upcoming season of The Amazing World of Gumball.

The season was confirmed[1]on LinkedIn by Emma Fernando, a former employee on the show.

The season's is scheduled to release somewhere between 2025-2026, as confirmed by an attendee at the three Warner Bros. Discovery animation studios' Studio Focus panel at Annecy[2], and EIDR listings have confirmed it will have the regular 40 episode length.[3]

Adam Long and Kerry Shale have both confirmed that Mr Small, Leslie, Larry and Bobert will all be returning[4]
